	Enemies of technology. Extremely durable and strong.

-+- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - + - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -+-
	The path of the Naturalist is the bane of technology. They hate machines
and distrust science vehemently. Their conviction about the evils of technology
drive them with a power bordering the miraculous. A Naturalists presence has 
often been suspected of being the lone cause behind mechanical failures of
all sorts. Cars stall, lights burn out, and bullets seem to never hit their mark.
Some believe Naturalists are really just Mystics of a more savage nature
