-+- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - + - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -+- 

	The Last Remnant of a tribe of powerful killers. They've had many 
names throughout their history --> Bullet Monk, Breathing Guns, and 6 hells.
No one knows their true origin. They were myth in the days of the first World
War. When the War of Wheels began they appeared and offered 'un-wheeled' empires
a fighting chance. The few still roaming are the remains of those empires failures.
Many have no clue about the war that broke their silence. Many have been trained
since then by the survivors, clueless of the legacy their skill descends from.

