-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Methods
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Double Up - weild 2 single handed weapons at the same time
Fast Reload - Cuts reload clicks in half
Duel Realod - Reload 2 Revolvers as if reloading 1
Beading Focus - For every click that a Gunslinger concentrates before each
	shot, that shot receives a + 1 bonus to aim. 
Range - Increased Revolver Range
Etch Bullets Dmg/Aim - By spending time (10 min per bullet) a gunslinger can
	carve patterns into his bullets to make them more lethal (Dmg) or
	more accurate (Aim). A Bullet cannot have more than one etching.
Called Shots - Bonus applied on all called shots
Faster Reload- Cuts reload clicks in half again 
Pistol Deflection - A Gunslingers guns act as small shields in his hands 
	granting armor bonus of +1 per Revolver euipped.
Bullet Storm - Allows Gunslingers to pull tiggers twice per click. Take a
	-8 to armor total for 6 clicks afterward.
Fast - +4 Initiative
Interruptor - Free interrupts on foes interrupts
Duel Etch - By Spending 8 hours per bullet a Gunslinger can carefully combine 
	2 etchings on a single bullet.
Hip Shots - No Bead penalty is now -5
Own The Clock - Everytime the Gunslinger interrupts he gets and extra click that
	round. This benefits even those interrupts granted from interrupts 

