Available Skills
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Skill*   *Mod Attribute*  *Description*
Gut            (WIS)     - Rely on your guy to get a sense of the situation
Star Sense     (WIS)     - Ability to infer meaning from the stars alignment
Meterology     (WIS)     - Ability to read the signs of the cosmos and predict patterns
Survival-Wild  (WIS)     - Ability to find food and resources in wild
Spot           (WIS)     - Spot hidden foes, objects, traps
Listen         (WIS)     - Hear them before they hear you
Mutantology    (INT)     - Knowledge of the mutant race
Religion       (INT)     - Knowledge of various religious practices
History        (INT)     - Knowledge of the past events
Diplomacy      (CHA/APP) - Ability to talk your way through a situation
Government     (INT)     - A keen understanding of Government structure
Law            (INT)     - Knowledge of the Law and loop holes
Sneak          (DEX/AGI) - Ability to move silent and unseen
Hide           (DEX)     - Ability to hide and stay hideen


